- What is this?

922
01:04:33,653 --> 01:04:34,696
<i>The Older Women Hunter?</i>

923
01:04:34,780 --> 01:04:36,114
You need to stop, ma'am.

924
01:04:36,198 --> 01:04:37,824
Please leave immediately.

925
01:04:38,658 --> 01:04:40,202
<i>Joo In-a couldn't possibly be</i>
<i>having an affair.</i>

926
01:04:40,494 --> 01:04:43,121
<i>Has she ever come with a man?</i>

927
01:04:43,205 --> 01:04:45,374
<i>Gosh, ten condoms?</i>

928
01:04:45,457 --> 01:04:48,835
<i>Our company is about to see</i>
<i>the biggest storm in history.</i>

929
